# Scripts and Styles Guide

- The [src/scripts](mdc:src/scripts) directory contains core JavaScript logic, utilities, and GUI managers.
  - Main entry: [main.js](mdc:src/scripts/main.js)
  - Utilities: [utils](mdc:src/scripts/utils)
  - GUI managers: [gui](mdc:src/scripts/gui)

- The [src/styles](mdc:src/styles) directory contains CSS files for the project.
  - Main stylesheet: [main.css](mdc:src/styles/main.css)
  - GUI styles: [gui](mdc:src/styles/gui)
  - Utility styles: [utils](mdc:src/styles/utils)

Use these directories for shared logic and styling across all apps.

